com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast

Interface IDateTime

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IFilterElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDateTimeField, IDateTimeInputArg, IDateTimeLiteral

    public interface IDateTime
extends IFilterElement
    Defines a common interface for all query elements that evaluate to date/time types. IDateTime instances can be acquired by using IQuery.newDateTimeArg() or by traversing through a query model to a date/time field.
    Since:
    0.5
